{"id": "1218758837717303457", "channel_id": "1215331353248272514", "type": 0, "author_id": "1164258265799086080", "author_name": "metam0n", "author_bot": false, "content": "「睡莲 - 宁菲亚」\n「睡蓮 - 寧菲亞」\n20240317\n\n简评：\n最时尚的小垃圾，最热门的颓丧，最朴素的中毒，宁菲亚也是广受好评的首领之一（咬牙切齿）。曾经大家都在想着怎么第一回合给她打进二阶段，现在我只能说少用点会生成症状的症状（呓语/臆想/盲从）。当你决定下回合弄死她的时候，手上的窒息就不用管了。\n路线规划几乎没有什么余地，新手打完落地战就觉醒，拐弯进商店再回头进传送门。第三场战斗打完先不要踩事件，最后回来踩可以删垃圾。", "timestamp": "2024-03-17T03:12:30.356000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [{"id": "1218758837356466227", "filename": "V4_-_-_20240317.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 1621222, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1215331353248272514/1218758837356466227/V4_-_-_20240317.jpg?ex=69cbe45e&is=69ca92de&hm=d91249c6ece54ed0061facfcf53f639bc6ac22f1afa83b7f290bf797479aa4d0&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1215331353248272514", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "幻梦深浅地图全解 第4版 死扛黑印分时代", "forum_channel_id": "1174179624096378930", "thread_tags": ["1181143392739147778", "1211882178007408651", "1174179680056791130"]}
{"id": "1218824669889560656", "channel_id": "1217679877906501733", "type": 0, "author_id": "1046407805260812350", "author_name": "z1473", "author_bot": false, "content": "拉蒙娜、溫科爾、汀克特、旺達\n\n曜令：腐朽盛筵\n\n活動關卡，黑印很多，玩起來比較舒服。\n\n拉蒙娜：工具人（銀曜充能、拉4費、刻印易傷）\n\n汀克特：工具人（減算力、解狀態，）\n\n溫科爾：\n工具人（2費銀曜充能，虛弱，\n幫旺達補狂氣，在超維空間能爆發兩次，讓臨時反擊最大化）\n\n旺達：\n4費，盡量依靠拉蒙娜拉牌疊反\n且夢引4以下\n最好能刻印「曜遷」\n拿來疊反，疊夢引用\n\n攻擊/防禦/3費，往超維空間丟\n其他人的牌，別去佔用超維空間\n\n然後進超維空間時候\n溫+旺達，夢引10以上\n讓臨時反擊疊到最高\n\n之後打3費。\nUid:100108744", "timestamp": "2024-03-17T07:34:05.969000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": "2024-03-29T00:30:34.019000+00:00", "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "🍟", "emoji_id": null, "count": 11}], "attachments": [{"id": "1218824669118070794", "filename": "Screenshot_2024-03-17-15-09-12-860_com.sialiagames.z1.gp.twnew.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 190674, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1217679877906501733/1218824669118070794/Screenshot_2024-03-17-15-09-12-860_com.sialiagames.z1.gp.twnew.jpg?ex=69cc21ad&is=69cad02d&hm=95590c0cffea32331cf461abb7d807408fac14dbe941c8401987dce6add0efb8&"}, {"id": "1218824669575254107", "filename": "Screenrecorder-2024-03-17-14-58-56-6040.mp4", "content_type": "video/mp4", "size": 13288590, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1217679877906501733/1218824669575254107/Screenrecorder-2024-03-17-14-58-56-6040.mp4?ex=69cc21ad&is=69cad02d&hm=342c20ccdec71410709381cd30db65063e2d8d312533a80a57a620e010a6517c&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1217679877906501733", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "💌「旺達」體驗交流分享活動💌", "forum_channel_id": "1174179624096378930", "thread_tags": ["1202451003690188860"]}
